  • High Resolution Settlement Layer (HRSL)

    Identify buildings distribution at a resolution of 1 arc-second (approximately 30 meters). This data is crucial for Maputo, where the distribution of the population has a very low detail.

    • In Accessibility, equity and social exclusion
